  - One tablet after food
  - One tablet three times daily
  - Two capsules after diarrhea
  - One capsule before breakfast
  - One tablet daily
  - One tablet every 24 hours
  - One tablet daily
  - One tablet before meals
  - One sachet twice daily
  warnings:
