  - Orajel
  descriptions:
  - Antibacterial mouthwash for fresh breath
  - Toothpaste for sensitive teeth
  - Helps reduce gum bleeding
  - Treats gum infections and inflammation
  - Used for cleaning between teeth
  - Relieves mouth ulcer pain
  - Treats oral fungal infections
  - Daily protection toothpaste
  - Supports gum healing and protection
  - Pain relief gel for mouth irritation
  dosages:
  - Use twice daily after brushing
  - Brush teeth twice daily
  - Use morning and evening
  - Rinse mouth for 30 seconds
  - Use once daily
  - Apply small amount on affected area
  - Apply inside mouth four times daily
  - Brush after meals
  - Apply directly on gums
  - Use as needed for pain relief
  warnings:
  - Do not swallow
  - Keep away from children
  - Avoid eating after use
  - Not suitable for children under 6
  - Use gently to avoid gum injury
  - Do not exceed recommended use
  - Consult doctor if symptoms continue
  - Store in cool dry place
  - Avoid contact with eyes
  - Stop use if irritation occurs
