  - Relieves muscle and joint pain
  dosages:
  - Apply twice daily
  - Apply as needed
  - Use 2 times daily
  - Apply thin layer daily
  - Use morning and evening
  - Apply after cleaning skin
  - Use at night only
  - Apply twice daily for 2 weeks
  - Use once daily
  - Apply 3 times daily
  warnings:
  - Avoid contact with eyes
  - For external use only
  - Do not apply on open wounds
  - Do not overuse steroid creams
  - Stop use if irritation occurs
  - Keep away from children
  - Use sunscreen with this product
  - Do not use on sensitive areas
  - Avoid prolonged use
  - Wash hands after use
